<p>After some feedback from some coworkers, there is an issue at the <em>AddContentEditorExtensions.cs</em> file. The problem is related to the <em>renderContentEditor&nbsp;</em>pipeline that is executed when Sitecore loads the Control Properties dialog.</p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="" /></p>
<p>The&nbsp;<a title="Issue-20" href="https://github.com/andresvillenas/Sitecore.Extensions/issues/20" target="_blank">Issue-20</a>&nbsp;was created to track the problem. The issue is already fixed and new version&nbsp;<a title="v0.0.2.1" href="https://github.com/andresvillenas/Sitecore.Extensions/releases/tag/v0.0.2.1" target="_blank">v0.0.2.1</a>&nbsp;was released. It should be available in the Sitecore Marketplace in the next days.&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="https://marketplace.sitecore.net/en/Modules/S/SitecoreExtensions.aspx">https://marketplace.sitecore.net/en/Modules/S/SitecoreExtensions.aspx</a></p>
<p>Please, take a look and create a new issue if there is a new problem.</p>
<p>That's it for today.</p>
<p>Until the next post!</p>
